2002-2149 (La. 10/25/02)

In re Appeal of DECISION OF DISCIPLINARY BOARD NO. 01-DB-188. No. 2002-OB-2149. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Levith, Neil P.; — Plaintiff; Applying for Appeal of the Decision of the Disciplinary Board, No. 01-DB-188.

Denied.

KIMBALL, J., to grant to consider Board’s authority regarding consent discipline.
